PERSONAL INFORMATION WE COLLECT AND OUR BUSINESS PURPOSES FOR COLLECTION
Personal information is information that identifies or relates to an identifiable individual. Through our Sites, Apps, and Solutions, subject to your consent if required by law, we may collect the following personal information for the business purposes listed in the table below:
From you or an EventOrganizer when you
create an account or register for an Event
using our Sites
