For most Events, we collect first and last name, email address, physical address, phone number, personal description or preferences, contact information of a friend (when you share this personal data with us), Event results, transaction information including payment information, and purchase history. ¬†For account creation we may also collect your date of birth, account credentials including password, and marketing and subscription preferences.
We use this information to contact you, process your order, manage payment, manage any contact you have with us about your purchase, analyze your personal characteristics and identify and recommend appropriate Events, for profiling and analytics (See ‚ÄúExplaining more about Marketing, Profiling and Automated Decision Making‚Äù section below for more detail), manage any dispute relating to a purchase, run analytics or collect statistics, and to communicate with you about your use of our Sites, Apps, and Solutions. If you make a purchase using a registered account, we will add this transaction to your profile so we can understand your interests and preferences and you will see a record of your transactions.
‚Äç
Our legal bases for using this information
include (1) your consent, (2) performance of a contract with you, (3) our legitimate interests which include to improve our Sites, Apps, and Solutions, better engage with you, prevent fraud, and secure our Sites, and (4) to comply with a legal obligation (to the extent we are required to retain information for compliance with applicable laws or regulations).
